5. Emergency Protocols

In the event of a Class-C Breach, the system enters Retraction Mode. All Scutes close, the Plastron severs external API ties, and the Ribs enter a read-only state until the operator manually resets the Core Neural Node.

Warning: Manual resets require a dual-key handshake between the Lead Developer and the System Owner.
